Find foo and replace with bar whole words and ask for confirmation

:/s/\<foo\>/bar/gc


Commenting :tim pop
vgc  
v for visual mode



To start using PHP auto completion, press the Ctrl + x followed
 by Ctrl + o keys while writing some PHP functions.
:set omnifunc=phpcomplete#CompletePHP

